Black wins the rook but he will have to waste valuable time getting his queen back in the game. In contrast white is almost completely mobilized and Black has not even castle yet. Black also has the problem of his light bishop being stuck on it original square. In conclusion white is doing better here and has more than enough compensation for the rook
